                              <p>HEAD OFFICE:</p>
                              <p>IDEAL TRADE CENTER,102,SHAHEEDTAJUDDIN AHMED SARANI,TEJGAON I/A,DHAKA-1208;TEL:9129396,9113161,9112539; FAX:880-2-8122181 ;E-mail:esquire@bangla.net</p>
